                    "text": "The avarek withdraws beneath its spines, presenting a defensive, spiky exterior. It gains a +2 circumstance bonus to spine Strikes and AC. Any adjacent creature that attempts a melee attack against the avarek takes 1d6 piercing damage per attack, regardless of whether the attack hits. Prickly Defense lasts until the avarek uses a <a aonid=\"114\" game-obj=\"Traits\">move</a> action or makes a Strike with any weapon other than its spines.",
